library("gganimate")
datasaurus <- readxl::read_xlsx("HW4_data.xlsx")

ggplot(datasaurus, aes(x = depth, y = phosphate)) +
  geom_point() +
  labs(x = "Depth", y = "Phosphate") +
  facet_wrap(block ~ .) +
  ggtitle("Data by Block") +
  theme_bw()

  ggtitle("Datasaurus GIF") +
